--------------------------------------------------------------------
	Installation Instructions
--------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Obtain the bundle from the aforementioned GitHub Repository:
	
	git clone git://github.com/uxp/Objective-C-Foundation-Tool.tmbundle
	
2. In Finder, double click "Objective-C Foundation Tool.tmbundle"
	to install the bundle in TextMate.
	

